<p>Out of respect to the people that have completed this quest (not an easy or fast one by any means) I think they should add another step: <br /> <br />Since Sony will want it to be tied into a new expansion... put a lost coldain in darkhollow or something. For storyline have it that he/she has lost faith. You hand your shawl to him/her and the faith is restored. He/she gives you back your new shawl upgraded with stats reflecting the current game. <br /> <br />The proposed quest is just a simple hand in because the effort was already there. This item always deserves to be a /drool thing. <br /> <br />I will pursue the current version some day :)</p>
