		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2"><a name="109882971215575"></a><span class="msgSubject">New Change</span><br clear="all" />
		   <span class="sm">Posted: Oct 26th  2004 at  6:28pm EDT<span class="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a class="sm" href="/db/item.html?item=11999;mid=109882971215575#post"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a> </span></span></td></tr>
