<td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%">
<p>As of 25 OCT 04, the latest change for this item is that the range of buffs that it extends has been increased.  Prior to yesterday it only worked on buffs that last 48 seconds or more and now it works on any buff that normally lasts 24 seconds. <br />There are not too many of those spells around that this affects, but it makes sense to have the change.</p>
