<p>First, FT 1 stacks with FT 1. If you have 7th shawl, and choker, of the wretched, and the solstice earring, you have a total of FT3. Supposedly, at one of the EQ conventions, the developers mentioned a cap on TOTAL FT items of 15. And yes there are items with FT higher than 5. However, if you have 3 items with FT7, you don't get 21 mana regen from it, you only get 15.</p>
