<td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%">
<p>An even easier updated way to do pottery with the lined poison vials is... Crow's Special Brew instead of Zombie Skin or animal hides.. In Abysmal Sea there is a merchant who sells the Brew in unlimited quantities. Just look up &quot;Special Brew&quot; on eqtraders.com and click the link for Crow's Special Brew. </p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td class="fs8"></td></tr></table></td></tr></table>
</div>

