<td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%">
<p>Side note for any KARANA worshipping char that is working on smithing.  Head to Surefall, hail Qaelin Hailstorm and get your FREE Mark of Karana.  Buy Small Bricks of Steel from same, then head to your fave forge.  Combine 1 file, Mark of Karana, 1 Small Brick of Steel, and 1 Flask of Water to make Steel Arrowheads. Triv to 188. WAY cheaper than doing Fine Plate.</p>
