<p>Did the shawl walk last night, and used the same method.  Worked perfectly! <br /> <br />A thing to note, if you have anyone helping you that is KoS to dwarfs, have them stay far far away from the general.  He has a fairly large agro radius and will slow you progression significantly if you have to wait for mem blurs after each agro. <br /> <br />Also, we ran him up near the next spawn point for the waves before we memblurred him and for 3 out of the 5 waves he just started up right where we blurred him.  The other two he had to walk back to his original pathing line and walk it for himself. <br /> <br />In all I think we had 12-15 people.  It went off without a hitch.</p>
